cleaned_text: Host Betsy Ashton and Dr. Paul Marik will be joined by Jay Naidoo, an elder statesman and lifelong freedom fighter who worked as an activist alongside Nelson Mandela during and after apartheid, for a discussion on the global tyranny he is seeing emerge at every level of society - and what each of us can do to confront it.
